Welcome
Armstrong Energy, through its 100% wholly owned subsidiary Armstrong Coal, is a leading producer of steam coal in the Illinois Basin. Armstrong controls over 565 million tons of proven and probable coal reserves and operates five mines in Western Kentucky. Armstrong ships coal to utilities via rail, truck and barge and has the capability to provide low cost custom blend coal to fuel virtually any electric power plant in the Midwest and Southeast regions of the nation. Armstrong is fully committed to the health and safety of its workforce and to compliance with reclamation and environmental standards.



