Armstrong Energy, Inc. Key Developments

Armstrong Energy, Inc. Amends and Restates the Certificate of Incorporation
Jun 7 17
Armstrong Energy, Inc. amended and restated the certificate of incorporation. The name of the Corporation is Armstrong Energy, Inc. The date of filing of its original Certificate of Incorporation with the Secretary of State of the State of Delaware was September 30, 2011. The Corporation was originally incorporated under the name Armstrong Land Company, Inc. This Amended and Restated Certificate of Incorporation of the Corporation, which restates, integrates and further amends the Certificate of Incorporation of the Corporation as heretofore amended, has been duly adopted by the Corporation's Board of Directors and by the stockholders in accordance with Sections 242 and 245 of the General Corporation Law of the State of Delaware.


Armstrong Energy, Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017; Provides Capital Expenditures Guidance for the Year 2017
May 12 17
Armstrong Energy, Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported revenue of $59,108,000 against $60,444,000 reported last year. Operating loss was $4,971,000 against $5,321,000 reported last year. Loss before income taxes was $15,446,000 against $13,324,000 reported last year. Net loss was $15,446,000 against $13,441,000 reported last year. Net loss attributable to common stockholders was $15,446,000 against $13,441,000 reported last year. Net cash used in operating activities was $2,011,000 against $2,202,000 reported last year. Investment in property, plant, equipment, and mine development was $1,205,000 against $947,000 reported last year. Adjusted EBITDA was $3,108,000 against $4,433,000 reported last year.

The company expects capital expenditures for 2017 to be in the range of $12.0 million to $16.0 million.


Armstrong Energy, Inc. to Report Q1, 2017 Results on May 12, 2017
May 2 17
Armstrong Energy, Inc. announced that they will report Q1, 2017 results at 9:00 AM, Eastern Standard Time on May 12, 2017


