Armstrong Energy, Inc.



 OVERVIEW



Date Founded


2006




Headquarters


7733 Forsyth Boulevard, Suite 1625, St. Louis, MO 63105




Industries


Coal

Holding Companies




Company Description


Armstrong Energy, Inc. engages in the production of low chlorine, high sulfur thermal coal from the Illinois Basin, with both surface and underground mines. The firm markets its coal primarily to proximate and investment grade electric utility companies as fuel for the steam-powered generators. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in St. Louis, MO.




Website


http://www.armstrongenergyinc.com






